re** → ✅ gần xong, cần push 17 commits + dọn repo\n2. **Migration script (ahv-openclaw-setup)** → đọc nội dung rồi báo cáo\n3. **Khác** → nói rõ hơn\n\nChờ Lead hướng dẫn tiếp."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":477,"output":565,"totalTokens":24430,"cacheRead":22455,"cacheWrite":933,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776226552335,"responseId":"062e43f9b5eb94d8ca5013359b1987c9","__openclaw":{"id":"6d34c150","seq":12}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:53c5832a-eecc-4d6b-a4c3-d1b78a430dca","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7","displayName":"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7","updatedAt":1776208566543,"sessionId":"26f7c499-7fac-499e-bf9f-921a2e2ab1b6","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":21354,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/26f7c499-7fac-499e-bf9f-921a2e2ab1b6.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have enough context. Let me compile the briefing.\n\nYesterday (2026-04-14):\n1. DTLX Backend Fix — `docs` vs `data` field mismatch fixed across all modules, 18/18 API endpoints verified ✅\n2. Pipeline degraded due to gateway timeout & Telegram delivery issues, but recovered to HEALTHY ✅\n3. Session cleanup — prior abort instances cleared ✅\n4. Students page filter bug fix ✅\n5. Cron jobs (5p progress + daily briefing) running ✅\n6. Telegram delivery instability resolved ✅\n\nToday (2026-04-15 in local time, but it's currently April 14 23:16 UTC = April 15 06:16 UTC+7):\n\n\nQLHV backend has a merge request pending Lead review, while AHV Works still needs P0 fixes and the Stitch MCP wrapper test plus stitch-connect skill update remain on the backlog. The pipeline is running clean with no active subagents, and both the DTLX backend and frontend are stable, though there's no current blocker aside from the Q